early and mid career mentoring & support lydia l sohn university of california berkeley page 1 early and mid career mentoring & support finding mentors and setting priorities lydia l sohn university of california berkeley page 2 the importance of mentoring internal mentor guide you through your department's maze can offer good suggestions on how to write grants help with the tenure process help build relationships with other colleagues both within your dept and elsewhere on campus page 3 external mentor can also help with grants gives you an outside and objective perspective on your career advancement can find out things informally for you helps promote you outside of your university page 4 whether you have a mentor or not two things to remember go to conferences write papers apply for grants and try not to take rejection personally it's ok to make a mistake
